titleHead: [CY] Cannot appeal - Appeal a benefit decision - GOV.UK
title: [CY] Unfortunately you can’t appeal
appealLateReason: [CY] If your appeal is late then you need to give a reason and you’ve told us you don’t have one.
findContactDetails: [CY] If you still think you’re entitled to benefits you can contact DWP. You can find their contact details on any letter you’ve received from them.
